OL,3,C'Behind the smile': Domestic abuse
OL,4,Ctraining for hair and beauty industry
OL,6,FHairdressers and beauticians across
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland have taken part in
OL,8,Fspecialist training to help them
OL,9,Frecognise the hidden signs of domestic
OL,10,Fabuse.
OL,12,FThe sessions were delivered in
OL,13,Fpartnership with the PSNI and Policing
OL,14,Fand Community Safety Partnerships
OL,15,F(PCSPs).
OL,17,FAround 50 local businesses heard from
OL,18,Fpolice, victim support agencies and
OL,19,Finput from lived experience at the
OL,20,Ftraining on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
