OL,3,C'Behind the smile': Domestic abuse
OL,4,Ctraining for hair and beauty industry
OL,6,FThe 'Behind the Smile' session focused
OL,7,Fon identifying coercive control.
OL,9,FIt is a form of abuse that can include
OL,10,Fmanipulation, isolation, monitoring,
OL,11,Fintimidation as well as physical abuse.
OL,13,FParticipants were told how to safely
OL,14,Frespond to concerns and signpost
OL,15,Fclients to support services.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
