PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774954972
OL,3,C'Behind the smile': Domestic abuse
OL,4,Ctraining for hair and beauty industry
OL,6,FSpeaking after the event, south
OL,7,FBelfast Area Commander Superintendent
OL,8,FFinola Dornan said: "Domestic abuse is
OL,9,Fnot always visible. Coercive control
OL,10,Fin particular can be subtle,
OL,11,Fpersistent, and deeply damaging.
OL,13,F"Hairdressers and beauticians are in a
OL,14,Funique position as they build trusted
OL,15,Frelationships and may notice changes
OL,16,Fothers don't.
OL,18,F"They may have a client who feels
OL,19,Fcomfortable in that safe space to open
OL,20,Fup and disclose abuse.
OL,26,@pD@UOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774954972
OL,3,C'Behind the smile': Domestic abuse
OL,4,Ctraining for hair and beauty industry
OL,6,F"This training is about giving them
OL,7,Fthe confidence to recognise the signs
OL,8,Fand know how to respond safely if that
OL,9,Fhappens."
OL,11,FShe added: "We know that domestic
OL,12,Fabuse affects people from all
OL,13,Fbackgrounds, and we want to ensure
OL,14,Fanyone experiencing abuse feels able
OL,15,Fto come forward and seek help. Trusted
OL,16,Fspaces can help uncover hidden harm."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@IO]sD@LOUxD@eO]
