OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774954972
OL,3,C'Behind the smile': Domestic abuse
OL,4,Ctraining for hair and beauty industry
OL,6,FRecent figures show that police in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland receive a domestic
OL,8,Fabuse call approximately every 16
OL,9,Fminutes, highlighting the scale of the
OL,10,Fissue.
OL,12,FThe PSNI have said they continue to
OL,13,Fencourage anyone experiencing abuse,
OL,14,For anyone concerned about someone
OL,15,Felse, to report it and that support is
OL,16,Favailable, and all reports are taken
OL,17,Fseriously.
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,20,FITVX
